data.description: Huge investments opportunity!!! Welcome to this corner lot well maintained and spacious multi family home in Irvington, ideal for both owner occupants and investors. The 1st floor unit offers 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, an eat-in kitchen, dining room and a living room. There's an extra space with a huge closet off of the living room that can be easily converted to a possible 3rd bedroom.The 2nd floor offers exactly the same layout as the 1st floor, with also the possibility of adding a third bedroom.The 3rd floor which is the finish attic is very spacious and has its own bathroom and and a separate entrance. This property has a full basement, half finished and 2 detached car garages. All separate utilities including an oil powered furnaces. Unit 1 has an above ground oil tank and Unit 2 has an underground oil tank. Great location, just minutes away from public transportation, restaurants, retail stores and a short drive to GSP, I-78. Take advantage of this opportunity and make this property yours.
